com.yahoo.bullet.rest.service

Class HandlerService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.bullet.pubsub.PubSubResponder
      • com.yahoo.bullet.rest.service.HandlerService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @Service
public class HandlerService
extends com.yahoo.bullet.pubsub.PubSubResponder
    This is used for synchronous sending and handling of queries. To store and manage QueryHandler instances.

      • failHandler

        public boolean failHandler(String id)
        Fail a given handler, if it exists. This does not submit anything to Bullet. It simply removes the handler and invokes its QueryHandler.fail() method.
        Parameters:
        id - The ID of a handler to fail, if it exists.
        Returns:
        true if the handler was failed.
